Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.62,0:02:18.61,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be1}茫茫人海行色匆匆　擦肩而过碰撞纠缠
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.81,0:02:24.73,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be1}感受彼此羽翼的伤痛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.06,0:02:30.92,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be1}用寂寞抱紧你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.51,0:02:37.37,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be1}无须其他任何表示
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.80,0:02:40.74,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be1}等候交融的瞬间　觉醒的永恒
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.93,0:02:43.79,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be1}心急如焚
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.26,0:02:50.32,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be1}时光荏苒转瞬即逝　
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.49,0:02:59.79,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be1}只能叹息　心愿遥不可及
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.05,0:03:06.09,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be1}炽热的灵魂　传递真情
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.21,0:03:09.29,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be1}不再有保留
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.45,0:03:15.64,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be1}你曾经的思念
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.39,0:03:20.92,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be1}又在何方…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,============================ED============================
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.72,0:22:37.28,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\be1}平凡的温柔　让你远去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.53,0:22:45.01,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\be1}被抛弃的心灵　四处彷徨
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.33,0:22:53.24,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\be1}这份失落　如果就是生活
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.44,0:22:57.52,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\be1}我愿在夜空下　从此闭上双眼
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.80,0:23:06.55,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\be1}曾形影不离　黄昏却已变色
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.80,0:23:17.77,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,1000)}{\be1}至少让我在月光下　静静入眠…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,============================Avant============================
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.52,0:00:08.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一层外装剥离
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.09,0:00:10.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,减速至4马赫
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.48,0:00:11.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,角度正常
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.60,0:00:13.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,28秒后停止强制冷却
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.01,0:00:15.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,启动姿态控制
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.36,0:00:19.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Alpha-1呼叫 各机检查弹药装填
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.34,0:00:20.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Bravo-2
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.18,0:00:20.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Charlie-3
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.07,0:00:21.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Delta-4
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.03,0:00:23.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二层外装剥离
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.68,0:00:27.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给那些地面上的家伙点颜色看
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.24,0:00:30.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穿过对流层
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.83,0:00:32.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,减速至0.9马赫
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.98,0:00:33.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷却停止
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.44,0:00:35.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姿态正常
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.91,0:00:38.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上天保佑我们
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.77,0:00:40.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,降落坐标锁定
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.02,0:00:43.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来吧 我们走！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.30,0:00:45.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为扎夫特而战
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.14,0:00:45.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为扎夫特而战
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.93,0:00:46.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为扎夫特而战
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.54,0:01:05.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,C.E.70年
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.73,0:01:07.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「血色情人节」的悲剧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.27,0:01:10.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,导致地球与PLANT的紧张关系
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.61,0:01:14.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最终升级为武力冲突
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.28,0:01:40.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战前无人怀疑
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.18,0:01:42.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地球军将以数量优势取胜
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.99,0:01:46.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 现实出乎所有人的预料
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.36,0:01:48.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战局陷入拉锯
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.41,0:01:51.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,转眼间 第十一个月即将过去…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,============================Main============================
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.08,0:03:28.95,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(1180,576)}{\fad(500,500)}{\bord3\shad1\be20\an3\fs60}虚假的和平
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.92,0:03:32.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,南非难民营中
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.89,0:03:35.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,食品等援助物资长期短缺
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.90,0:03:39.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,120万人挣扎在生死线上
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.60,0:03:44.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下面是高雄激烈战事的后续报道
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.48,0:03:52.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,据最新消息 扎夫特军上周
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.63,0:03:54.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在高雄以北六公里处…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.70,0:03:55.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基拉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.29,0:04:01.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来你在这里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.15,0:04:04.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加藤教授在到处找你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.83,0:04:05.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又找我？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.89,0:04:08.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要我们捉你去见他
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.79,0:04:11.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么 又被拉去当苦力了？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.75,0:04:16.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是 昨天接的还没做完呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.47,0:04:19.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}快快 赶快跑
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.83,0:04:20.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噢！有什么新消息？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.06,0:04:23.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 高雄的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.78,0:04:28.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从距离高雄7公里的郊外传来激烈交火声
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.85,0:04:30.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上周就这样的话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.18,0:04:33.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在已经陷落了吧 高雄
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.43,0:04:35.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.41,0:04:40.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高雄离本土很近 本土不会有事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.90,0:04:43.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用担心
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.13,0:04:46.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,近归近 可我们是中立国
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.63,0:04:49.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奥布才不会变成战场呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.16,0:04:52.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 但愿…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.45,0:04:59.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会真的发生战争的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.02,0:05:01.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,PLANT和地球之间
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.67,0:05:07.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我想避难没什么意义
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.72,0:05:10.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过基拉马上也会来PLANT吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.49,0:05:16.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基拉？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.72,0:05:18.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发什么呆呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.44,0:05:20.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还不快走
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.48,0:05:22.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.10,0:05:26.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,修正轴线 右6.51刻度
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.51,0:05:27.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,矢量正常
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.71,0:05:30.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停止制动喷射
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.69,0:05:32.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,转为磁导控制
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.02,0:05:36.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,减速率2.56
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.77,0:05:38.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停船 原地待命
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.00,0:05:42.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这艘船也算完成它最后的使命了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.07,0:05:46.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一路护航辛苦 弗拉戈上尉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.42,0:05:50.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪里话 所幸途中平安无事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.64,0:05:53.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,附近扎夫特舰船的动向如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.54,0:05:55.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有两艘在跟踪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.55,0:05:59.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不怕 进了港扎夫特也没辙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.64,0:06:02.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只因为是中立国吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.01,0:06:04.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想想真是好笑
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.60,0:06:08.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是拜它所赐 计划才顺风顺水
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.19,0:06:11.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说明奥布终究还是地球上的国家
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.20,0:06:13.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舰长 我们告辞了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.84,0:06:24.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让他们自己上岸 不会有事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.81,0:06:28.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再菜也是「G」的选拔机师
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.19,0:06:30.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.54,0:06:33.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你去了反而引人耳目
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.12,0:06:45.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别一副为难的表情 阿迪斯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.72,0:06:47.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.34,0:06:50.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等待议会答复后也不迟…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.95,0:06:50.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就迟了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.47,0:06:53.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的直觉这样告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.41,0:06:56.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在此错过机会的话
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.75,0:07:00.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其代价 必将用你我的性命来偿还
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.41,0:07:03.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地球军的新型机动兵器
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.95,0:07:06.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必须在它们转移之前夺取
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.24,0:07:10.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听我说 不是这样的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.50,0:07:14.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还不承认 快老实交代吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.14,0:07:14.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.64,0:07:19.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米丽雅莉娅
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.99,0:07:20.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,HI
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.45,0:07:23.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米丽雅莉娅应该听说了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.68,0:07:25.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.81,0:07:27.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别说啊 真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.72,0:07:31.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她收到赛·阿盖尔的情书了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.44,0:07:33.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,却想瞒着我们
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.68,0:07:37.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们闹够没有
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.27,0:07:43.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不上车的话 可以借过吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.91,0:07:45.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 请
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.94,0:07:51.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不理你们了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.71,0:07:52.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.08,0:07:54.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.73,0:07:57.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,顺路去佛罗伦萨蛋糕店吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.25,0:08:00.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能还有限量的咖啡卷
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.78,0:08:04.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,写情书了 赛这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.82,0:08:09.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到啊 你也看上芙蕾·阿尔斯塔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.81,0:08:11.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 对手很强劲哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.22,0:08:13.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基拉·大和同学
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.44,0:08:15.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才没有…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.44,0:08:21.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真够和平的 这里
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.39,0:08:27.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相同年龄 有的孩子已经上前线了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.21,0:08:53.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么关系 你问不出口的话
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.51,0:08:56.59,up,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(200,200)\fs32}（曙光社3号门）
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.41,0:08:55.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去替你问
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.39,0:08:57.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说过不用了 多尔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.58,0:09:02.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加藤学术会学生三人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.79,0:09:03.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切换为跟踪模式
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.16,0:09:12.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中午好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.39,0:09:17.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 基拉你可算来了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.71,0:09:26.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.63,0:09:28.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 教授的客人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.03,0:09:30.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说是教授让他在这里等
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.13,0:09:33.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 教授人呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.38,0:09:46.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是给你的 追加内容
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.92,0:09:48.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.45,0:09:51.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过不问也知道 无非是曙光社的项目
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.35,0:09:55.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本不感兴趣 改良系统参数
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.50,0:09:58.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正就是程序分析
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.29,0:10:10.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谈重点 快问情书的事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.37,0:10:11.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,情书？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.09,0:10:14.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.20,0:10:15.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能没事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.92,0:10:23.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.75,0:10:25.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事没事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.35,0:10:26.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底什么事 多尔
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.26,0:10:27.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偷偷告诉我 偷偷告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.30,0:10:28.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.34,0:10:30.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放开 憋死了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.62,0:10:31.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可不行
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.95,0:10:34.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时间到了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.03,0:10:37.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拔锚 梅萨琉斯号出发
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.42,0:10:57.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是 赫利奥波利斯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.24,0:11:00.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正在驶近的扎夫特舰 请回话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.65,0:11:02.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,扎夫特舰请回话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.69,0:11:03.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空管部长
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.47,0:11:06.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷静 把警报给我关了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.25,0:11:10.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告知正在驶近的扎夫特舰
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.25,0:11:15.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贵舰已经严重侵犯我国主权
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.83,0:11:17.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要求你们立即停船
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.67,0:11:19.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,扎夫特舰 要求你们立即停船
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.20,0:11:21.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高强度电波干扰
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.86,0:11:23.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是扎夫特舰船放出的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.83,0:11:26.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是明显的战斗行为
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.26,0:11:46.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.94,0:11:47.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两艘
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.23,0:11:49.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纳斯卡和劳拉西亚级
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.38,0:11:53.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,电波干扰前一刻已经释出机动战士
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.70,0:11:56.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让路易斯和盖尔在梅俾斯上待命
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.54,0:11:58.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先别出击
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.85,0:11:59.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舰长…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.78,0:12:02.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别慌 轻举妄动会中敌人圈套
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.71,0:12:05.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交给赫利奥波利斯应对
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.05,0:12:08.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,推进燃料充填完成80%
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.69,0:12:11.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第16工作组开始装载物资
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.65,0:12:18.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道 该走时我们自然会走
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.01,0:12:21.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,召回拉米亚斯上尉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.73,0:12:23.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始「G」的搬运工作
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.33,0:12:23.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.86,0:12:32.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打下矿山后直接占领内部
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.17,0:12:32.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.85,0:12:56.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,运去大天使号 快
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.86,0:13:15.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陨石？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.92,0:13:22.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弗拉戈上尉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.80,0:13:25.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让船出动 港口会被占领
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.31,0:13:27.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也出击
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.82,0:13:48.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,扎夫特军两架机动战士 入侵七号区
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.19,0:13:54.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.73,0:13:55.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,机动战士？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.33,0:14:04.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是那个
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.97,0:14:06.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被克鲁泽队长言中了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.58,0:14:10.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戳他们一下就慌忙跑出巢穴
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.52,0:14:14.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自然人果然够蠢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.45,0:14:19.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像发现宝贝了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.58,0:14:21.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,S区 第37厂区
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.12,0:14:22.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收到
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.11,0:14:25.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是伊扎克 干净利落
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.51,0:14:51.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,盖尔
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.06,0:15:00.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉米亚斯上尉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.33,0:15:03.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们和舰长失去联络 情况不明
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.72,0:15:13.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,扎夫特的！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.40,0:15:16.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让X105和303启动
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.20,0:15:18.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把它们开出厂区
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.06,0:15:19.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.77,0:15:28.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么 外面发生什么了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.41,0:15:34.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.38,0:15:36.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鬼知道
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.47,0:15:37.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在被扎夫特攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.18,0:15:40.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,机动战士到卫星里来了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.92,0:15:41.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们也快走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.26,0:15:44.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.00,0:15:45.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们走
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.62,0:15:50.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基拉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.50,0:15:51.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马上就回来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.05,0:16:13.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,带不走的工厂设施和零件全部就地摧毁
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.53,0:16:16.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,报告说有5架啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.29,0:16:18.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剩下的2架还在里面吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.15,0:16:20.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和拉斯提的小队去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.95,0:16:22.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊扎克你们负责这边的3架
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.76,0:16:23.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,OK 交给我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.59,0:16:26.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,登机后先解除自爆装置
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.39,0:16:42.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想去哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.77,0:16:43.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是那边
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.20,0:16:45.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要跟来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.49,0:16:46.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你自己还不快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.38,0:17:01.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女…孩子？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.30,0:17:04.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你以为是什么？ 刚才
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.75,0:17:05.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.72,0:17:08.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别管我 快走
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.37,0:17:11.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有要确认的事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.81,0:17:13.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这时候你让我往哪里走
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.50,0:17:14.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经回不去了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.80,0:17:18.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.09,0:17:18.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这边！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.79,0:17:19.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放手 你这个傻瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.09,0:17:20.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傻…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.34,0:17:24.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早说过会这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.91,0:17:27.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事 会得救的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.48,0:17:30.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,厂区那里还有避难所
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.71,0:18:06.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这…这是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.24,0:18:09.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.25,0:18:12.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地球军的新型机动兵器
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.83,0:18:16.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲大人这个叛徒！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.27,0:18:20.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开什么玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.50,0:18:24.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孩子？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.93,0:18:27.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别哭了 跑起来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.52,0:18:37.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呵 这玩意儿还不赖嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.84,0:18:38.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样 提亚哥
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.98,0:18:40.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,OK 开始更新
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.13,0:18:42.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重筑数据链接
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.56,0:18:43.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完成自检
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.38,0:18:45.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以启动
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.55,0:18:50.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尼科尔
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.86,0:18:53.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍等 还有少许
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.23,0:18:57.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿斯兰和拉斯提呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.08,0:18:58.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好慢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.55,0:19:00.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就少替他操心了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.41,0:19:03.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先带走这3架
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.13,0:19:06.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交到克鲁泽队长手上前可别弄坏了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.40,0:19:22.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看吧 大家都在这里避难
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.32,0:19:24.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外面还有人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.95,0:19:27.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 请让我和朋友也进来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.64,0:19:28.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托开门
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.86,0:19:29.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两个人？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.84,0:19:30.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.26,0:19:32.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里已经人满为患了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.61,0:19:37.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,左边有37号避难所 知道怎么走吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.00,0:19:41.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个人也好 请让她进去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.21,0:19:43.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是个女孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.15,0:19:45.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.78,0:19:48.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,进去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.89,0:19:52.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.68,0:19:54.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别说了 快进去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.88,0:19:55.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去对面
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.63,0:19:58.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的 快
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.47,0:20:00.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 你…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.20,0:20:10.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉米亚斯上尉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.84,0:20:13.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈玛拉 布莱亚 快启动它
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.94,0:20:18.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当心背后
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.14,0:20:26.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才的孩子 怎么会？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.29,0:20:32.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快走
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.36,0:20:35.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去左区的避难所
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.42,0:20:36.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别管我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.85,0:20:38.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那里只剩门了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.99,0:20:46.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这边
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.01,0:20:58.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉斯提！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.06,0:21:03.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈玛拉！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.46,0:21:31.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿斯兰…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.93,0:21:33.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基拉？
